<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">I have been trying to get in contact with you regarding your business insurance renewal.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">As your policy is not in auto renewal, it is currently due to expire on&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(insert expiry date)</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Once your Kingsbridge insurance policy has expired</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, if you don't have another insurance policy in place&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your business may not be covered against claims</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">To help you stay protected, we recommend exploring either a renewal or alternative cover options. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to me on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Can I still make a claim once my policy expires?</b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Use for Admiral if holding PI)</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;Your package of insurance includes Professional Indemnity cover. This element of the policy works on a ‘claims made’ basis, meaning&nbsp;</span><u style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">you must have cover in place at the time of the claim and not at the time of the incident for your policy to provide cover</u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Use if holding PI)&nbsp;</i><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><u>If you choose to cancel your Kingsbridge insurance policy and do not hold alternate cover elsewhere your business will not be covered</u></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;against claims of negligence.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Use for Admiral)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Any claims for the&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(delete as appropriate)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Public Liability, Employers’ Liability, Contract Works, Own Plant and Hired in Plant elements for the time your policy was active&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>(DD MMM YYYY to DD MMM YYYY)</b>&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">can be notified to insurers. Please refer to your policy wording for full information.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you are unsure whether you can make a claim on a expired policy, please contact our customer service team and they will be happy to help.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>